Ordinary Member

Sapioclub ordinary members are siblings with annual membership subscription with the club and are entitled to several benefits of the club amongst which are entertainment, events, shopping, health, business, hotels and a lots more.

Platinum Member

Sapioclub platinum members are exceptional people who have either be selected after review from the stakeholders or rather must have been invited/reffered by three(3) existing platinum members for review consideration before being selected.
